snippet.title: Cosmic Horror Tales - Official Trailer -
snippet.description:
Trailer for Cosmic Horror Tales, a top down horror pixel art game about finding your lost chicken Petunia. Face the horrors that away you in Old Liam's Farm as you uncover a cult and discover an ancient evil. 

This title will release on steam soon.
